  "baseRefName": "main",
  "body": "## What changed\n\nBuilt a complete company operating system to position Dealix as an AI Business Operating Systems company for Saudi B2B.\n\n### Safety gates (Phase 1)\n- \\\"scripts/verify_no_auto_external_send.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/verify_repo_large_files.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/verify_secret_patterns.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/verify_outreach_compliance.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/verify_company_launch_ready.py\\\"\n- Makefile targets: \\\"company-check\\\", \\\"launch-check\\\", \\\"no-auto-send-check\\\", \\\"large-file-check\\\", \\\"secret-check\\\"\n\n### Company OS docs (Phase 2)\n- \\\"docs/company/DEALIX_COMPANY_OS_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/DEALIX_COMPANY_OS_EN.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/FOUNDER_DAILY_OPERATING_SYSTEM_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/SERVER_OPERATING_MODEL_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/AI_VENDOR_ROUTING_STRATEGY_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/SECURITY_PRIVACY_TRUST_MODEL_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/DELIVERY_PLAYBOOK_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/CLIENT_ONBOARDING_PLAYBOOK_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/PROOF_LEDGER_PLAYBOOK_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/SAUDI_MARKET_POSITIONING_AR.md\\\"\n\n### Daily revenue machine (Phase 3)\n- \\\"data/outreach/saudi_icp_segments.json\\\"\n- \\\"ledgers/prospects.csv\\\" (updated with source_url/verification_status/confidence)\n- \\\"ledgers/*.example.csv\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/revenue/run_daily_revenue_machine.py\\\"\n- Scoring, outreach, follow-up, proposal, daily CEO report scripts\n\n### 100 companies/day workflow (Phase 4)\n- \\\"docs/company/DAILY_100_TARGETS_WORKFLOW_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/revenue/prepare_100_target_day.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/revenue/validate_100_target_day.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/revenue/batch_outreach_queue.py\\\"\n\n### Gmail drafts only (Phase 5)\n- \\\"scripts/email/create_gmail_drafts_safe.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/email/gmail_drafts_runbook.md\\\"\n- Tests: \\\"tests/test_no_auto_external_send.py\\\", \\\"tests/test_gmail_drafts_only.py\\\"\n\n### Server readiness (Phase 6)\n- \\\"docs/server/DEPLOYMENT_RUNBOOK_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/server/ENV_CONTRACT_PRODUCTION_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"docs/server/RAILWAY_OR_SERVER_CHECKLIST_AR.md\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/server/server_preflight.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/server/server_healthcheck.sh\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/server/verify_env_contract.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/server/verify_public_surfaces.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/server/run_production_smoke.sh\\\"\n\n### Command center (Phase 7)\n- \\\"scripts/command_room/build_command_room.py\\\"\n- \\\"reports/command_room/index.html\\\"\n- \\\"docs/company/COMMAND_ROOM_RUNBOOK_AR.md\\\"\n\n### Sales assets (Phase 8)\n- One-pagers, email/WhatsApp templates by sector, discovery script, objection handling, proposal template, pricing ladder, case-study template, CEO intro message in \\\"sales/\\\"\n\n### Presentations (Phase 9)\n- \\\"presentations/dealix_company_profile_ar.html\\\"\n- \\\"presentations/dealix_company_profile_en.html\\\"\n- \\\"presentations/dealix_one_page_offer_ar.html\\\"\n- PDF export instructions (no browser/LibreOffice found in Codespace)\n\n### Compliance + trust (Phase 10)\n- PDPL outreach checklist\n- Email outreach safety policy\n- Client data handling policy\n- AI output review policy\n\n### Tests (Phase 11)\n- \\\"tests/test_company_launch_suite.py\\\" (17 tests)\n- \\\"tests/test_no_auto_external_send.py\\\"\n- \\\"tests/test_gmail_drafts_only.py\\\"\n\n### One-command execution (Phase 12)\n- \\\"scripts/run_company_launch_day.py\\\"\n- \\\"scripts/run_company_launch_day.sh\\\"\n- Makefile target: \\\"make company-day\\\"\n\n## How to run\n\n1. Daily:\n   \\\"\\\"\\\"bash\n   make company-day\n   \\\"\\\"\\\"\n2. Review drafts:\n   \\\"\\\"\\\"bash\n   ls outbox/2026-06-15\n   \\\"\\\"\\\"\n3. Open command room:\n   \\\"\\\"\\\"bash\n   open reports/command_room/index.html\n   \\\"\\\"\\\"\n4. Run tests:\n   \\\"\\\"\\\"bash\n   .venv/bin/pytest tests/test_company_launch_suite.py tests/test_no_auto_external_send.py tests/test_gmail_drafts_only.py -q\n   \\\"\\\"\\\"\n\n## What is safe by design\n\n- No automatic external send; all drafts require human review.\n- Opt-out line included in every generated message.\n- Max 3 follow-ups and 7-day cooldown enforced.\n- source_url required for every target.\n- No scraping; manual research workflow documented.\n- Secrets only via env vars; secret scanner passes.\n\n## What remains manual\n\n- Sending emails/WhatsApp (copy draft, review, send).\n- Updating ledgers/outreach_log.csv and ledgers/reply_log.csv.\n- Updating deals_pipeline.csv after meetings.\n- Setting Gmail OAuth env vars to create drafts via API.\n- Setting production env vars (APP_SECRET_KEY, DATABASE_URL, etc.).\n\n## Server readiness\n\n- \\\"make server-preflight\\\" passes Alembic and no-auto-send checks.\n- Fails on missing env vars in this Codespace; set APP_SECRET_KEY + DATABASE_URL for PASS verdict.\n\n## Daily founder routine\n\n- Morning: make company-day + review command room + review drafts.\n- During day: manual sends + update ledgers.\n- Evening: update pipeline + review daily CEO report.\n\n## Test results\n\n- 22 tests passed.\n- \\\"make company-check\\\" returns DEALIX_COMPANY_LAUNCH_READY=1.\n- \\\"make company-day\\\" runs end-to-end; verdict NEEDS_SERVER_FIX only because production env vars are not set in Codespace.\n\n## Risks\n\n- Files may be large to review; focus on scripts/revenue, scripts/email, scripts/server, docs/company, and tests.\n- Existing pre-existing staged modifications (not part of this PR intent) are present on the branch.\n- PDF export requires Chrome/LibreOffice/wkhtmltopdf not installed in Codespace.\n\n## Next steps\n\n1. Set production env vars and re-run make company-day for green verdict.\n2. Review and manually send first 10 drafts.\n3. Export PDFs from presentations/ when tooling available.\n4. Scale: 10 → 25 → 50 → 100 companies/day using BATCH_SIZE.\n",
